        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Hospital Price Transparency and Disclosure Act</b><br> <br> This bill specifies the format that hospitals must disclose the standard charges for items and services by requiring them to submit such charges to the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) and requiring the CMS to post the charges on its website.</p>]]></text>
